{"claim_id": "claim_001", "text": "MESSES is a Python package that facilitates the conversion of tabular data into other formats.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "MESSES (Metadata from Experimental SpreadSheets Extraction System) is a Python package that facilitates the conversion of tabular data into\nother formats.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_messes/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [1092, 1246], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.3390/metabo11030163", "spine_entity_ids": ["MESSES_system"]}
{"claim_id": "claim_003", "text": "The convert command transforms JSON format to the JSON version of supported formats and then to the final niche format.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "the convert command was designed to transform the JSON format described in the \n:doc:`experiment_description_specification` to the JSON version of any of the supported formats and then to the final \nniche format.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_messes/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [2127, 2339], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.3390/metabo11030163", "spine_entity_ids": ["convert_command"]}
{"claim_id": "claim_004", "text": "The convert command supports simple JSON-to-JSON conversion through the \"generic\" sub-command.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "The convert command also supports simple JSON-to-JSON conversion through the \n\"generic\" sub-command.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_messes/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [2340, 2440], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.3390/metabo11030163", "spine_entity_ids": ["convert_command"]}
{"claim_id": "claim_008", "text": "The extract command supports turning tabular data into JSON by adding a layer of tags on top of the data.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "The extract command of MESSES supports turning tabular data into JSON. \nThis is done by adding a layer of tags on top of the data.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_messes/synthesized_package", "source_section": "methods", "page": null, "char_span": [47452, 47582], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.3390/metabo11030163", "spine_entity_ids": ["MESSES_system", "extract_command"]}
{"claim_id": "claim_018", "text": "The override field in conversion directives allows direct specification of a string value.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "To simply specify the string value directly use the \"override\" field.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_messes/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [1818, 1876], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.3390/metabo11030163", "spine_entity_ids": ["override_field"]}
{"claim_id": "claim_019", "text": "The code field in conversion directives allows Python code to be delivered directly to eval().", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "What is in the code field will \nbe delivered directly to eval(), and the name of the internal variable for the input \nJSON is \"input_json\".", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_messes/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [5775, 5914], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.3390/metabo11030163", "spine_entity_ids": ["code_field"]}
{"claim_id": "claim_020", "text": "The for_each field in str directives allows looping over all records in a table.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "If the information to build the value is spread across several records, then use the \n\"for_each\" field to loop over all the records in the table", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_messes/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [11359, 11503], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.3390/metabo11030163", "spine_entity_ids": []}
{"claim_id": "claim_021", "text": "The delimiter field in str directives specifies how to separate strings built from each record.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "Use the \"delimiter\" field to specify the \ndelimiter to use.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_messes/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [11571, 11630], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.3390/metabo11030163", "spine_entity_ids": []}
{"claim_id": "claim_022", "text": "The test field in str directives filters records based on field equality conditions.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "Use this as a filter to filter out records that should not be used to build \nthe string value.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_messes/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [20955, 21049], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.3390/metabo11030163", "spine_entity_ids": []}
{"claim_id": "claim_023", "text": "The sort_by field in str directives allows sorting input JSON records before building the value.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "**sort_by** - a list of fields to sort the input JSON records by before building the value from them.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_messes/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [3547, 3644], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.3390/metabo11030163", "spine_entity_ids": []}
{"claim_id": "claim_024", "text": "The matrix directive creates a list of dictionaries by looping over all records in the indicated table.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "By default, this directive will loop over all records in the indicated table \nand build a dictionary for each record.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_messes/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [22795, 22912], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.3390/metabo11030163", "spine_entity_ids": ["matrix_directive"]}
{"claim_id": "claim_025", "text": "The collate field in matrix directives groups record data into dictionaries based on a specified field value.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "If given, the \nrecord data will be grouped into dictionaries based on their field value.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_messes/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [30226, 30314], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.3390/metabo11030163", "spine_entity_ids": ["collate_field"]}
{"claim_id": "claim_026", "text": "The fields_to_headers field changes matrix directive behavior to copy all fields from input records as is into the dictionary.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "The \"fields_to_headers\" field changes the behavior of the matrix directive so that \nby default all fields from input records are copied as is into the dictionary.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_messes/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [38164, 38326], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.3390/metabo11030163", "spine_entity_ids": ["matrix_directive", "fields_to_headers_field"]}
{"claim_id": "claim_027", "text": "The exclusion_headers field in matrix directives allows excluding specific fields from being added.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "The \n\"exclusion_headers\" field can then be used to exclude fields from being added.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_messes/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [38327, 38410], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.3390/metabo11030163", "spine_entity_ids": []}
{"claim_id": "claim_028", "text": "The values_to_str field in matrix directives can convert all field values to strings.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "The \"values_to_str\" field can also be used to convert all of the field values to strings.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_messes/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [5169, 5243], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.3390/metabo11030163", "spine_entity_ids": []}
{"claim_id": "claim_029", "text": "The required field in conversion directives indicates if a directive is required, stopping the program on error if true.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "**required** - a boolean or string value (\"True\" or \"False\") that indicates if the directive is \nrequired. If true, then errors encountered will stop the program.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_messes/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [21787, 21949], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.3390/metabo11030163", "spine_entity_ids": []}
{"claim_id": "claim_030", "text": "The default field in conversion directives provides a string value to default to if the directive cannot be built and is not required.", "claim_type": "explicit", "source_excerpt": "**default** - a string value to default to if the directive cannot be built and is not required.", "source_anchor": {"source_path": "/Users/nothiasl/git/AgenticScienceBuilder/outputs/asbb_pilot/coll_messes/synthesized_package", "source_section": "intro", "page": null, "char_span": [3829, 3916], "figure_id": null, "table_id": null}, "source_type": "text", "evidence_type": "knowledge", "trace_status": "exact_match", "evidence_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000302", "source_type_uri": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000311", "super_pattern": null, "source_doi": "10.3390/metabo11030163", "spine_entity_ids": []}
